[Client / Salesforce]
      ↓ POST /api/logs/error
[FastAPI ingestion -> normalized ] ->    --persist--> [Postgres]
      ↓ publish            ↓
   Kafka topic: error_events

                                         ↓ consumed by
                                     [Orchestrator Worker(s)]
                                          - run the workflow
                                          - store results -> Postgres
                                          - publish -> orchestrator_results topic
[Agents API] (optional) <--- read results from DB / orchestrator_results